data.description: Welcome to this stunning property! A grand entrance takes you into the open living area which is the hub of the home with a stunning stone fireplace as the focal point. Entertain in a well-appointed gourmet kitchen that boasts SS double oven, gas cooktop, vegetable sink in the large island, abundant counter space, and walk in pantry. Functional laundry room has a closet and cabinetry. Half bath is downstairs for guests. Primary bedroom is private with lots of light, ensuite bathroom with jetted tub, dual sinks, and generous closet.  Upstairs bedrooms have a jack n jill bathroom and extra storage closet. Bonus area with a desk and bookcases a great spot to read or study. Media room, provides an ideal space for family movie nights or game days.The balcony is great place for a quiet morning coffee to watch the sunrise. The backyard has a covered patio it's a place you can enjoy the serenity and seclusion of your outdoor space. Excellent schools and conveniences are close by!
